Package fetchData

Class DataObject

java.lang.Object
fetchData.DataObject
public class DataObject
extends java.lang.Object
A stack-based class that stores a set of values that correspond to a range of years.

Similar to a stack, this class can (provided a starting year) push and pop values. Years are added/removed at the end of the range, thus if the range is 1993-2008 and a value is pushed, it corresponds to the value in 2009. Date: 4/2/2021

Author:
Cameron Arnold
